battery_properties.notes: The FB200-1600 is a 200kW-1600kWh vanadium redox flow battery. Since it is a AC-connected system, it must be modeled with a free system converter that is 100% efficient and very large. No other components may be placed on the DC bus. Please refer to the technical documentation available on the website for detailed information.

flywheel_properties.notes:
Powercorp has over 20 years of experience in remote power generation and control.
Powercorp's proven success in this area has been achieved with high penetration wind diesel systems. With Powercorps PowerStore grid stabilising technology installed these systems can achieve in excess of 90% wind penetration without the need of batteries.
